 1,'Policy delivery and review cadence drive retention and referrals.',142),
('ultimate-critical-cover','study','closing','Ultimate goal of a CI closing conversation?',
 '["Hit target","Earn long-term advisory relationship via suitable, fully-understood recommendation","Max commission","Close fastest"]'::jsonb,
 1,'Sustainable practice prioritises trust and suitability.',143),
